                    <h3>Project Description</h3>
                    <p>
                        The game is an realistic FPS game that features both bounties that progress the main story and
                        boast high payouts, or exploration of
                        the world, where you can meet unique NPC's and do side activities to prepare for the next bounty
                        or side quest that progress your relationship with your crew.
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        The realism aspect of the gameplay is to do with gunplay and damage, where each combat encounter
                        is deadly and requires smart decision making and planning to complete effectively. Guns have
                        realistic recoil and feel heavy and brutal, as if each shot makes an impact to the world or
                        other characters.
                        <br>
                        <br>
                        The open world exploration allows the player to walk around the level and take in scenery,
                        complete hits or side bounties, talk to unique NPC's, find secrets or trade. Unique NPC's can
                        give side storylines, items or even be a fight the player has to go through.

                    </p>
